Naked <a href="Nazi_crimes_against_Soviet_POWs" title="Nazi crimes against Soviet POWs">Soviet POWs</a> in Mauthausen concentration camp. Between June 1941 and January 1942, the Nazis killed an estimated 2.8 million <a href="Red_Army" title="Red Army">Red Army</a> POWs, whom they viewed as "subhuman".<sup id="cite_ref-116" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-116"><span>[</span>116<span>]</span></a></sup></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:%22Colored%22_drinking_fountain_from_mid-20th_century_with_african-american_drinking.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4a/%22Colored%22_drinking_fountain_from_mid-20th_century_with_african-american_drinking.jpg/220px-%22Colored%22_drinking_fountain_from_mid-20th_century_with_african-american_drinking.jpg" width="220" height="151" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4a/%22Colored%22_drinking_fountain_from_mid-20th_century_with_african-american_drinking.jpg/330px-%22Colored%22_drinking_fountain_from_mid-20th_century_with_african-american_drinking.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4a/%22Colored%22_drinking_fountain_from_mid-20th_century_with_african-american_drinking.jpg/440px-%22Colored%22_drinking_fountain_from_mid-20th_century_with_african-american_drinking.jpg 2x" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
